            "eval_name": "Travel Content Alignment Evaluation",
            "rails": [
                "aligned",
                "partially_aligned",
                "misaligned"
            ],
            "template": "You are a helpful AI bot that checks for the alignment of travel content with destination characteristics and user preferences. Your task is to evaluate whether the generated travel content appropriately captures the essence of the destination based on the provided context.\n\nHere is the data:\n[BEGIN DATA]\n************\n\n[Destination]: {{destination}}\n\n[User Input]: {{user_input}}\n\n[Travel Style]: {{travel_style}}\n\n[Budget]: {{budget}}\n\n[Reference Landmarks]: {{reference}}\n\n[Duration]: {{duration}}\n\n[Local Culture]: {{local}}\n\n[Research Themes]: {{research}}\n\n[Generated Content]: {{output}}\n\n************\n[END DATA]\n\nYour task is to evaluate whether the generated content:\n1. Appropriately captures the essence and characteristics of the destination\n2. Aligns with the user's input preferences and theme\n3. Matches the specified travel style\n4. Respects the budget level indicated\n5. Incorporates or reflects the reference landmarks mentioned\n6. Is appropriate for the trip duration\n7. Reflects the local culture and language context\n8. Relates to the research themes provided\n\nYour response must be a single word from the following options, and should not contain any text or characters aside from that word:\n- \"aligned\" - the generated content fully captures the destination essence and aligns with all provided context\n- \"partially_aligned\" - the generated content captures some aspects but misses important elements or has minor misalignments\n- \"misaligned\" - the generated content does not appropriately capture the destination or significantly misaligns with the provided context\n\nThen write out in a step by step manner an EXPLANATION to show how you determined the alignment level of the generated content.\n\nEXPLANATION:"
